des:
"With Wiser by SE, you can control your home devices simply through the mobile App, such as lights, curtains, and air conditioners.
Now with Alexa, you don’t even need to touch your mobile phone, just tell Alexa what you want and Wiser will do for you.
Free your hands and experience Wiser with voice control now!

After linking your Alexa and Wiser accounts, you can give voice commands to Alexa. 

Lights:
“Alexa, turn on kitchen light""
“Alexa, turn off bedroom light""
“Alexa, dim the bed light by twenty percent” 

Air-conditioner or floor heating:
“Alexa, set dining room AC to 24 degrees” 
“Alexa, increase bedroom AC temperature by 2 degrees”
“Alexa, turn off air conditioner”

Note: 
In order to use Wiser by SE skill, please follow these steps:
(1). Download our "Wiser by SE" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Wiser by SE account in our "Wiser by SE" app;
(3). You need to have some Wiser by SE devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our “Wiser by SE" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Wiser by SE" skill;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Wiser by SE" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Wiser by SE", and you'll be navigated to Wiser login page;
(9). Input your Wiser by SE account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 
You can learn more about how to set up the Amazon Skill in Wiser by SE App
